casebody.data:
No. 205,

Misc.

Johnson et al. v. New Jersey. M. Gene Haeberle, Stanford Shmukler and Curtis R. Reitz for petitioners. Norman Heine for respondent.

Sup. Ct. N. J. Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari granted. The case is transferred to the appellate docket and set for oral argument immediately following No. 80, Misc.
